Good afternoon, this mac suffered oxidation, I performed the cleaning in the tests off in the middle of the boot. I cleaned the ME region. the system boots, but with intermittence. I analyzed the board again, I identified the missing <CAPACITOR>C2450</CAPACITOR>, I put another one in place, but I'm still locked in the logo. 
In the ASD test, I diagnose with no defect.

